Module org.nothing.jocularweather
Package org.nothing.jocularweather

Record Class Report

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
org.nothing.jocularweather.Report
Record Components:
coord - location of station
weather - qualitative overview of weather
base - internal parameter
main - quantitative weather containing temp, pressure, humidity
visibility - measured visibility in meters, capped at 10km
wind - wind data at station
clouds - cloud coverage at station
rain - recent rainfall history at station
snow - recent snowfall history at station
dt - current time formatted as Unix timestamp (UTC)
sys - static positional and solar data of station
timezone - time correction from UTC in seconds
id - identification number of city
name - name of town
cod - internal parameter
All Implemented Interfaces:
ReportBase
public record Report(org.nothing.jocularweather.Coordinates coord, List<org.nothing.jocularweather.Weather> weather, String base, org.nothing.jocularweather.Details main, int visibility, org.nothing.jocularweather.Wind wind, org.nothing.jocularweather.Clouds clouds, org.nothing.jocularweather.Rain rain, org.nothing.jocularweather.Snow snow, int dt, org.nothing.jocularweather.WxSystem sys, int timezone, int id, String name, int cod) extends Record implements ReportBase
Parent class for JSON object from weather report. Follows API docs here. This implementation assumes that everything is okay; all usages of the class are initialized with the ReportType.OKAY type or otherwise deferred to the MalformedReport type.
